# Force LF line endings for the submitted scripts.
#
# The development host is Windows (core.autocrlf=true), which would
# otherwise check these files out with CRLF line endings. A CRLF on the
# shebang line makes the Linux/Docker test environment fail with
# "bad interpreter: /bin/bash^M", so the scripts are pinned to LF.
clean   text eol=lf
analyse text eol=lf
